291
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,056
DUE TO THE RUMORS THAT
ARE CURRENTLY A HOT TOPIC

292
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,920
WE WILL BE PAUSING
UPDATES ON THE GROUP'S NEWS

293
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:44,200
All right. I’ll head back now.

294
00:21:48,600 --> 00:21:49,600
I have to go.

295
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:51,800
Our fanbase account decided to rest.

296
00:21:54,360 --> 00:21:55,360
