297
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,640
BAIFERN

298
00:22:13,680 --> 00:22:14,920
PO

299
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:31,120
WHAT’S WRONG?

300
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:34,000
WHY DID YOU CLOSE YOUR ACCOUNT?

301
00:22:46,520 --> 00:22:47,920
- Hello? - Fern,

302
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,680
why did you close your account?

303
00:22:50,280 --> 00:22:51,680
Do you think I wanted to do that?

304
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:54,120
I didn’t want to do it either.

305
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:56,016
But I'm mentally breaking down right now.

306
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:57,040
Do you understand?

307
00:22:58,320 --> 00:22:59,920
Don’t let your emotions take over, okay?

308
00:23:00,280 --> 00:23:01,600
You're running a fanbase account.

309
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:05,240
Shutting it down all of
a sudden has a big impact.

310
00:23:05,320 --> 00:23:08,920
It'll seem like Sphere
will stop supporting them.

311
00:23:09,520 --> 00:23:13,840
Po, when I became his
fan, I followed my heart.

312
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:15,600
Now that I'm mentally breaking down,

313
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:17,320
can't I follow my heart too?

314
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:26,600
Did you do what I asked you to?

315
00:23:28,520 --> 00:23:30,120
Are you really going to use this method?

316
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,000
Yeah.

317
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:34,000
I already told Per about
this when he came back.

318
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:38,360
We have to protect both
our dreams and our love.

319
00:23:42,600 --> 00:23:44,480
No matter what, we have
to make it work, right?

320
00:23:49,600 --> 00:23:50,840
But what Thame said is right.

321
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:53,120
Because of Pepper’s scandal,

322
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,880
