323
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:57,080
True.

324
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:58,920
I already scrolled through it.

325
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:01,160
People are really searching
for our group's name more.

326
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:04,840
It seems they want to know
who we are and what we do.

327
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:07,400
And it seems to have an
impact on our song, too.

328
00:24:08,120 --> 00:24:09,920
A scandal doesn’t only
have negative effects,

329
00:24:12,120 --> 00:24:13,600
but it creates buzz too.

330
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:15,680
The point is,

331
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:18,000
how do we turn it to our advantage?

332
00:24:19,120 --> 00:24:20,320
Are you saying

333
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:23,640
we should push the buzz

334
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:25,560
about why idols aren't allowed to love?

335
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:29,240
This is actually the question
people have always been asking.

336
00:24:29,320 --> 00:24:32,560
They’re already wondering if it’s fair
for idols to not have their private lives.

337
00:24:33,560 --> 00:24:35,200
What if they throw a question back at us?

338
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:38,960
Like, if you knew the rule from the start,

339
00:24:39,040 --> 00:24:41,480
