362
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:56,240
Previously,

363
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:59,200
we were their everything.

364
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:04,280
But now, I’m no longer sure

365
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:09,400
what we actually are to them.

366
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:17,080
Hey.

367
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:19,320
Let me tell you something.

368
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:23,000
From filming their documentary
for some time already,

369
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:26,880
I can tell there’s no way
they will love you guys less.

370
00:26:29,240 --> 00:26:30,280
Do you know why?

371
00:26:31,840 --> 00:26:35,000
That’s because you’re part of their dreams,

372
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:39,280
