381
00:27:16,760 --> 00:27:18,080
Activate your account, okay?

382
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:21,720
Only you can help him.

383
00:27:22,800 --> 00:27:24,040
You know well

384
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:26,920
