understand this whole thing.

385
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,200
And I bet you know better than I do

386
00:27:30,040 --> 00:27:31,280
that during this time,

387
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:35,440
it’s really easy for
anti-fans to ruin them.

388
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:41,800
Fine. I get it now.

389
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:44,000
I’ll reopen the account now.

390
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:47,000
But can you tell them something for me?

391
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:51,920
Let them take action. Anything will do.

392
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:54,680
He can either admit or deny it.

393
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:58,920
