394
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:04,400
Uh-huh. I now understand
what Thame is about to do.

395
00:28:04,480 --> 00:28:06,416
You’re appearing on a show
to promote your song, right?

396
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:08,800
