you’re avoiding their questions.

400
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:18,840
But if you want to answer, go ahead.

401
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:21,240
We’ve been well prepared for this anyway.

402
00:28:21,320 --> 00:28:23,200
We’ll hold hands and
get through this together.

403
00:28:24,840 --> 00:28:27,200
I’ll help check the buzz for you guys.

404
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:29,000
Things will turn out well. Trust me.

405
00:28:29,520 --> 00:28:30,720
By the way,

406
00:28:30,800 --> 00:28:32,760
