461
00:31:23,040 --> 00:31:24,440
That’s Miss Gam.

462
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:26,440
Whoa. I can’t believe it.

463
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:28,120
There’s a huge age gap.

464
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:32,440
