465
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:35,520
They’re digging up her
info as if she killed someone.

466
00:31:36,080 --> 00:31:37,360
You’re right.

467
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,760
It’s Miss Gam?

468
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:02,360
She didn’t pick up my call.

469
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:05,400
She must be running an errand or something.

470
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:22,000
- Hello? - Hello, Thame?

471
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,160
It’s Gam.

472
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:30,040
Why didn’t you pick up Per’s call?

473
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:36,280
Well, I just finished the meeting.

474
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:39,616
