a press conference, right?

478
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:58,720
But before that,

479
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:00,720
give me some time to talk to Per.

480
00:33:35,360 --> 00:33:37,680
Hello, members of the press.

481
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:40,160
We’d like to thank
everyone for being here today

482
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,600
to attend this press conference

483
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:43,880
and hear our side of the current issue

484
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:48,160
