with the woman in the photo.

487
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:58,320
Pepper will personally
clarify the situation.

488
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:12,880
I’m Pepper, from MARS.

489
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:21,120
I would like to apologize
for everything that happened,

490
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:24,840
and I would like everyone to rest assured

491
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:32,600
that she and I are no longer together.

492
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,440
Let’s break up.

493
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:51,480
Are you talking about us
pretending to break up for now?

494
00:34:53,520 --> 00:34:54,960
This is your new plan, right?

495
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:58,920
No.

496
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:05,680
I’m talking about a real breakup, Per.

497
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:07,880
Gam!

498
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:12,840
Regarding the person in the photo,

499
00:35:14,160 --> 00:35:15,480
I admit that

500
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:17,960
we were in the talking stage for a while,

501
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,360
but there's nothing between us now.

502
00:35:33,120 --> 00:35:34,120
Why?

503
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:36,520
Is it because of the leaked photos?

504
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:42,560
But you told me that though it’s
leaked, it’d be fine, didn’t you?

505
00:35:46,520 --> 00:35:48,000
Before this, it was fine,

506
00:35:48,720 --> 00:35:50,360
but actually, it isn’t.

507
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,840
Hold on.

508
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:57,720
But you told me we’d never
let go of each other’s hands.

509
00:35:58,880 --> 00:36:01,760
My members and I have been
trying every possible way.

510
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:04,040
I…

511
00:36:08,600 --> 00:36:12,160
It wasn’t easy for me to build
myself up to where I’m today.

512
00:36:12,240 --> 00:36:14,336
So, is it fair for random
people to tear me down like this,

513
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:16,080
as if I murdered someone?

514
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:19,360
Gam.

515
00:36:21,840 --> 00:36:25,200
Don’t listen to those comments, okay?

516
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:28,320
We don’t know their identities.
We don’t even know if they’re real.

517
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:31,320
But if affects my job

518
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:32,800
and the people in my company.

519
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:34,600
That’s why I need to care.

520
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:40,800
Now, our relationship is
simply that of good colleagues.

521
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:44,440
Lately, it's been other teams

522
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:46,720
from that company handling
work with MARS instead.

523
00:36:47,320 --> 00:36:49,920
As for the leaked photos
circulating on social media,

524
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:53,400
they were taken late last year.

525
00:36:54,840 --> 00:36:56,400
As for the photos at the event,

526
00:36:57,040 --> 00:36:59,480
it’s true they were taken
three months ago, but by that time,

527
00:37:00,240 --> 00:37:01,720
there was nothing between us anymore.

528
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:05,280
You have things you need to protect,

529
00:37:06,440 --> 00:37:07,800
and so do I, Per.

530
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:15,960
I’d like to ask everyone
not to bring her up anymore,

531
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:20,120
as she is not a public figure like I am.

532
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:23,560
I’ve been trying so hard
to become who I am today.

533
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:27,600
I can’t stand losing it.

534
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:30,440
I…

535
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:31,880
I’m sorry.

536
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:34,440
And most importantly…

537
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:38,880
But I just can’t handle
this kind of pressure anymore.

538
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,880
Right now, she and I…

539
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,400
are no longer involved with each other.

540
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:10,080
In my heart now,

541
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:14,640
apart from my members,

542
00:38:17,240 --> 00:38:18,840
there is only our Sphere.

543
00:38:28,560 --> 00:38:31,560
It's unfortunate that this scandal
came out during your comeback.

544
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:34,200
I’m fine,

545
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:38,040
but our fans must be so shocked.

546
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:42,640
Let’s consider the
latest song we just released

547
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:46,960
as both a declaration of love and
a comforting message from all of us.

548
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:49,640
Please accept it.

549
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:02,720
All right, everyone.

550
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:05,040
I hope that today, we've
cleared up all the issues.

551
00:39:05,120 --> 00:39:07,240
Thank you so much for today.

552
00:40:01,720 --> 00:40:03,160
I thought you wouldn’t come.

553
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:05,640
You want to talk to me, don’t you?

554
00:40:06,920 --> 00:40:07,920
Yes.

555
00:40:09,040 --> 00:40:10,720
What do you want to talk about? Go ahead.

556
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:15,120
I just don’t get it,

557
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:18,040
