558
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:23,480
Thame has figured out a way, hasn’t he?

559
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:26,000
And…

560
00:40:26,720 --> 00:40:30,720
I heard that you also agreed.

561
00:40:36,160 --> 00:40:38,720
Actually, I think Thame’s
solution might work out.

562
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:45,400
- But why… - But it takes time.

563
00:40:48,160 --> 00:40:49,920
And this huge amount
of time would stop them

564
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,760
from hitting number one on every chart.

565
00:40:54,200 --> 00:40:57,640
Having to carry me along like this
will prevent them from succeeding.

